headline: Are Wall Street Analysts Bullish on Extra Space Storage Stock?
summary: While Extra Space Storage has lagged behind the broader market over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.

headline: Should Extra Space Storage Stock Be in Your Portfolio Pre-Q4 Earnings?
summary: EXR is set to report Q4 2025 results on Feb. 19, with revenues anticipated to rise year over year, while FFO per share is expected to remain flat.
